text: A member of the Okeechobee County Commission in Florida promoted a claim that using a blow dryer could cure people of COVID-19.
entity_strings: COVID-19, Florida, Okeechobee County, blow dryer

text: Using a hair dryer to breathe in hot air can cure COVID-19 and stop its spread.
Breathing hot air from a hair dryer or in a sauna can prevent or cure COVID-19
